nodes.text: This clone trooper was part of a mission to Oznek circa 22 BBY, under the command of Clone Sergeant Banks. After crashing their LAAT/i gunship, the clone troopers were forced to camp in the planet's jungles. The next day, they undertook a mission to destroy a supposed droid command center. While trekking through the jungle, this clone was attacked and eaten alive by a carnivorous animal.
